Heat oil in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat and cook steak, stirring frequently, 6 minutes or until almost done. Remove steak; keep warm. Add Recipe Ready Broccoli Stir Fry and continue cooking, stirring frequently, 4 minutes or until vegetables are tender. Add back steak and stir-fry sauce and cook, stirring frequently, 2 minutes or until heated through.** Serve over prepared rice and sprinkle, if desired, with chopped peanuts.